videos.description: Journey Brown breaks multiple tackles and refuses to be brought to the ground, eventually scoring the 32-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State's Brown refuses to go down on 32-yard TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Penn State's Brown refuses to go down on 32-yard TD

videos.description: Memphis' Patrick Taylor Jr. dives for the 3-yard touchdown to quickly retake the lead over Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor dives for the Memphis TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Taylor dives for the Memphis TD

videos.description: KJ Hamler catches a screen and streaks up the sideline, eventually being ruled out of bounds at the one-yard line. On the next play, Noah Cain rushes for the 1-yard touchdown to put Penn State on top.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hamler's nice gain leads to Cain TD for Penn State) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Hamler's nice gain leads to Cain TD for Penn State

videos.description: Sean Clifford passes to Pat Freiermuth who shows no mercy when trucking a defender, setting up Devyn Ford to score the two-yard touchdown on the next play for Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Freiermuth trucks a defender, setting up TD for Penn State) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Freiermuth trucks a defender, setting up TD for Penn State

videos.description: Penn State's Journey Brown speeds through the secondary and no one has a chance to catch him as he scores the 56-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown breaks free for 56-yard Penn State TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Brown breaks free for 56-yard Penn State TD

videos.description: Memphis quarterback Brady White throws an absolutely perfect pass right to Damonte Coxie for the 41-yard gain, which set up Kenneth Gainwell's two-yard touchdown run a couple play later.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis' White drops a 41-yard dime that leads to TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Memphis' White drops a 41-yard dime that leads to TD

videos.description: Memphis wide receiver Kedarian Jones passes to quarterback Brady White who weaves his way to the one-yard line, setting up his quarterback sneak into the end zone on the next play for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis Special sets up Tigers' TD) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Memphis Special sets up Tigers' TD

videos.description: Memphis quarterback Brady White loses control of the ball as he is getting sacked, resulting in an interception returned for a touchdown by Penn State's Garrett Taylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State gets pick-6 on bizarre play) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Penn State gets pick-6 on bizarre play

videos.description: Noah Cain rushes for the one-yard touchdown to give Penn State a 53-39 lead with 6:31 remaining in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Cain's TD gives Penn State 2-score lead late

videos.description: James Franklin gets doused in Gatorade and takes exception by executing a perfect form tackle on the player responsible.
